```

Typicky flow s plannerem:
```python
plan = planner.plan(query)           # 3 sub-queries
exec_result = execution.execute(plan) # retrieval pro kazdy krok
all_chunks = exec_result.all_chunks() # flatten + dedup
answer = answer_service.generate(query, all_chunks)
```

