## 5. JAK SPOUSTET

### 5.1 Scraper

```bash
python app/main.py
# → vypise pocet parsovanych vysledku
# → ulozi results.json
```

### 5.2 FastAPI server

```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn[standard]
uvicorn app.api_app:app --reload
# → http://localhost:8000/docs  (Swagger UI)
# → POST http://localhost:8000/api/rag/search
```

Test endpointu:
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/rag/search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"query":"únos dítěte Rusko","top_k":5}'
```

### 5.3 Docker

```bash
docker build -t nalus-scraper .
docker run --rm nalus-scraper
```

### 5.4 Qdrant (lokalne)

Qdrant bezi na `localhost:6333`. E2E testy automaticky skipnou pokud neni dostupny.

Qdrant v Dockeru:
```bash
docker run -p 6333:6333 qdrant/qdrant
```

