### 6.6 Architektura testu

- zadne mocky na urovni service — pouze na urovni externich zavislosti (Qdrant, sentence-transformers)
- `MagicMock` pro Qdrant client a CrossEncoder model
- `_SpyLLM`, `_FixedLLM`, `_FailingLLM` pattern pro testovani LLM vrstev
- `caplog` fixture pro overeni trace logu
- session-scoped fixtures v e2e pro efektivni seeding Qdrantu

